column4:
In the next #COVID19 package, among other things we must provide smart, targeted support to:
➡️spur the economy &amp; incentivize folks to return to work safely;
➡️support our health care efforts to combat #COVID19;
➡️provide more $ &amp; flexibility to state and local governments;.....

The previous 5 #COVID19 bills have included initiatives I’ve supported:
➡️rebate checks &amp; expanded UI to help folks who lost jobs;
➡️PPP for small businesses &amp; Fed lending to keep employees;
➡️more $$ to support our health care response;
➡️education $ to help our kids &amp; schools.
